[09:14.69]	And do invite you to my sister's view,
[09:17.70]	Whither straight I'll lead you.
[09:20.23]MARK ANTONY	Let us, Lepidus,
[09:21.66]	Not lack your company.
[09:23.58]LEPIDUS	Noble Antony,
[09:24.87]	Not sickness should detain me.
[09:27.33]	[Flourish. Exeunt OCTAVIUS CAESAR, MARK ANTONY,
[09:27.75]	+ and LEPIDUS]
